      "DialogueText_10_10D44AC44144EC85326507BD9E2D1C2A": "NSLOCTEXT(\"\", \"507E2A70454A60B4DB3AF5B519D531DA\", \"Exactly. And, if your hunch is right and it really is Hyperion Crystal down there in that cavern we found, you can use it to make the electronics we need to create one!\")",
